; Coverage for commodity.cc date presence comparison
; One lot with date, other without - tests the asymmetric date paths
; The lot without date sorts first (left no date, right has date)

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/01/01]
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/15 Buy More
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$150.00}
    Assets:Checking

test bal --lots Assets:Brokerage
       5 AAPL {$150}
10 AAPL {$150} [2024/01/01]  Assets:Brokerage
end test
